<Base
  title="Plain Text vs HTML for Cold Email: Which Gets More Replies?"
  description="Plain text wins for cold email: it matches the structural fingerprint of one-to-one mail, avoids the HTML/image signals filters associate with bulk marketing, and consistently out-replies designed templates."
  schema={schema}
